Syntax: stun

Attempts to stun your current combat opponent, temporarily incapacitating
them and interrupting their actions. Stun targets whoever you are currently
fighting -- no argument is needed.

A successful stun leaves the target unable to act for a short duration,
giving you a window of uncontested attacks.

Restrictions:
  - Must be in active combat (fighting someone).
  - Only players (not NPCs) can use the stun command.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp stun bash trip dirt
